  "name": "Clockwork Rejuvenator",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p><strong>Activate</strong><span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> or <span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> Interact</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong> The round you activate the rejuvenator, you must first spend either 1 or 2 Interact actions to wind the device.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>This device has four finger-like latches centered around a whirring mass of gears.</p>\n<p>After winding the <em>clockwork rejuvenator</em>, you can latch it to the chest of an adjacent recently dead creature and return it to life. If you wound the rejuvenator using 1 Interact action, you can return to life a creature that died in the last 2 rounds, restoring it to 1 HP. If you wound the rejuvenator using 2 Interact actions, you can return to life a creature that died within the last 3 rounds. After attaching, the device continues to whirl for 1 minute, restoring 10 HP per round to the target. Thereafter, the <em>clockwork rejuvenator</em> loses its magic and becomes inert.</p>"
